      (add_le_add (norm_image_sub_le _ _ _) ((q.1 - p.1).le_opNorm p.2))
    _ ≤ (‖p‖ + 1) * Fintype.card ι * (‖p‖ + 1) ^ (Fintype.card ι - 1) * ‖q - p‖ +
