/-- Given a map `f : G →ₗ[𝕜] MultilinearMap 𝕜 E G'` and an estimate
`H : ∀ x m, ‖f x m‖ ≤ C * ‖x‖ * ∏ i, ‖m i‖`, construct a continuous linear
map from `G` to `ContinuousMultilinearMap 𝕜 E G'`.

