which is a linear map from `ContinuousMultilinearMap 𝕜 E G` to `MultilinearMap 𝕜 E' G'`. -/
def mkContinuousLinear (f : G →ₗ[𝕜] MultilinearMap 𝕜 E G') (C : ℝ)
