/-- If a multilinear map in finitely many variables on normed spaces satisfies the inequality
`‖f m‖ ≤ C * ∏ i, ‖m i‖` on a shell `ε i / ‖c i‖ < ‖m i‖ < ε i` for some positive numbers `ε i`
